He's the number-one high school fighter
in this town.

00:12:07.352 --> 00:12:09.020
He's fearless and meticulous.

00:12:18.821 --> 00:12:20.281
- Hello?
- <i>Hi, Seokcheol.</i>

00:12:20.365 --> 00:12:22.158
Tell me where Seokkyung is staying.

00:12:22.242 --> 00:12:24.160
What? Why do you ask?

00:12:24.244 --> 00:12:25.245
Hey, you punk.

00:12:25.328 --> 00:12:28.539
If a friend asks you something,
just give him an answer.

00:12:29.207 --> 00:12:31.834
- Then, let me ask you something too.
- What is it?

00:12:31.918 --> 00:12:34.045
Yesterday, my boss...

00:12:35.630 --> 00:12:36.631
Tsk!

00:12:37.173 --> 00:12:39.884
Gosh, forget it.
An underling like you wouldn't know much.

00:12:40.593 --> 00:12:44.138
<i>I'll text you the address.</i>
<i>Go find your first love.</i>

00:13:04.075 --> 00:13:05.910
