my first love?

00:13:48.494 --> 00:13:49.746
It's me, Byeongsoo.

00:13:50.246 --> 00:13:51.330
Byeongsoo?

00:13:55.460 --> 00:13:56.669
Goodness gracious.

00:13:57.920 --> 00:13:59.172
